{"tid":1660062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支01][亮劍!]《聯早》引學者：中國有能力反制　但未到公布的時候","createTime":"2019-10-17T09:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:24:17.000Z","uid":178875,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"bdaff0a8a5e8c93927a441279c4a536093d26e99","tid":1660062,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d86db278ca53c195e97bb86.jpg/q9O62mRWzRJkG2zF00jCIQAjL2EuhoXHQWak00FmpNM?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d86db278ca53c195e97bb86.jpg%2Fq9O62mRWzRJkG2zF00jCIQAjL2EuhoXHQWak00FmpNM%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=d1e43292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d3d0a538ca53c195e978f13.jpg/aRdipz6XNIEyt8q4cTokRguC4qfR1rOCyf3G58n9xuc?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d3d0a538ca53c195e978f13.jpg%2FaRdipz6XNIEyt8q4cTokRguC4qfR1rOCyf3G58n9xuc%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=b1ef639f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上海學者：「自由港」地位若受損 美企蒙巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n上海國際問題研究院港澳研究室主任張建則認為，中方不是沒有力量和手段反制，只是還沒有到公布的時候。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，香港是美國最大的貿易順差來源地，香港的自由港地位倘若因法案受損，美國企業將蒙受巨大損失。而中國備用的反制選項可包括，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">限制對華不友善的美國政客入境</span>香港和中國大陸，<br />\n限制美國通過香港為在<span style=\"color: red;\">亞太的美軍力量補給</span>，<br />\n限制<span style=\"color: red;\">美國資本通過香港進入大陸</span>的渠道等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Bp9EFn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Bp9EFn&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=9dacd3d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Bp9EFn</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講都唔知美軍經過亞洲要申請許可<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e3868f436cb5cf2e2e31c052d9e5f7829bbdd5","tid":1660062,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"<bloc